"1  (8-ounce) bag frozen green peas, thawed","1 cup fresh basil leaves","2 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil","12  (1/4-inch-thick) slices French bread baguette, toasted","1/4 cup part-skim ricotta cheese","1/2 ounce very thinly sliced prosciutto, torn into 12 equal pieces","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper"